com.epimorphics.lda.bindings
Class Bindings

java.lang.Object
  com.epimorphics.lda.bindings.Bindings
All Implemented Interfaces:
Lookup
public class Bindings
extends Object
implements Lookup

A Bindings maps variables (identified by their string names) to their Value (a lexical form with type & language annotation). It also has a set of parameter names, which correspond to the query parameter names, and can map partial resource names to their URLs.
